### list tasks 
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by name
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?name=Project HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by due date range 
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?dueDateFrom=2025-12-15T23:59:59.000Z HTTP/1.1

### Filter tasks by name and due date
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?name=api&dueDateFrom=2025-12-15T23:59:59.000Z&dueDateTo= HTTP/1.1

### Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/69d5960ef07334cc27d97bd5 HTTP/1.1

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NodeJs and Mongoose tests",
  "description": "Create comprehensive tests for all endpoints",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-15T23:59:59Z",
  "completed": false
}

### Update a task 
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/69d5960ef07334cc27d97bd5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Complete project setup",
  "description": "MongoDB and Task model completed successfully",
  "dueDate": "2025-11-30T23:59:59Z",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a task 
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/69d661991988eab22ae5b2c9 HTTP/1.1
